description:
https://www.playstation.com/accessories/playstation-portal-remote-player/

Make breaktime playtime with your own handheld gateway to ASTRO's supersized adventure*.

In your time of gaming need, stay connected to your PS5® console with the PlayStation Portal™ remote player.

Bring ASTRO's actions and awesome abilities to life with support for immersive haptic feedback and dynamic trigger effects. And take in each colorful world through a bright, and expansive 8" 1080p display, capable of delivering silky-smooth gameplay at up to 60fps**.

With the power to play your PS5 games over Wi-Fi* with console-quality controls, every breaktime can become playtime.

*ASTRO BOT game sold separately. PlayStation Portal remote player can stream compatible games installed on your PS5 console. PlayStation Portal remote player requires broadband internet Wi-Fi with at least 5Mbps for use. For a better play experience, a connection of at least 15Mbps is recommended.
